    <item>
      <title>标准普尔 500 强公司通过从收益中剥离更多项目来提高利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/s-p-500-companies-adjust-gaap-net-income-for-more-items-boost-eps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的分析发现，美国大型公司正在通过从净利润中排除诉讼费用和无形资产摊销等项目来提高调整后的每股收益，尽管监管机构正在审查此类做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/s-p-500-companies-adjust-gaap-net-income-for-more-items-boost-eps</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
